-------------------------------------
Test File Types
bats-file/README.md
-------------------------------------
Check if a file or directory exists!
- assert_exists
- assert_not_exists

Check if a file exists!
- assert_file_exists
- assert_file_not_exists

Check if a directory exists!
- assert_dir_exists
- assert_dir_not_exists

Check if a link exists!
- assert_link_exists
- assert_link_not_exists

Check if a block special file exists!
- assert_block_exists
- assert_block_not_exists

Check if a character special file exists!
- assert_character_exists
- assert_character_not_exists

Check if a socket exists!
- assert_socket_exists
- assert_socket_not_exists

Check if a fifo special file exists!
- assert_fifo_exists
- assert_fifo_not_exists

-------------------------------------
Test File Attributes
bats-file/README.md
-------------------------------------
Check if file is executable!
- assert_file_executable
- assert_file_not_executable

Check the owner of a file!
- assert_file_owner
- assert_file_not_owner

Check the permission of a file!
- assert_file_permission
- assert_not_file_permission

Check the size of a file by bytes!
- assert_file_size_equals

Check if a file have zero bytes!
- assert_size_zero
- assert_size_not_zero

Check the groupID of a file!
- assert_file_group_id_set
- assert_file_not_group_id_set

Check the userID of a file!
- assert_file_user_id_set
- assert_file_not_user_id_set

Check if a stickybit is set!
- assert_sticky_bit
- assert_no_sticky_bit	

